Privacy Policy

Last updated: March 26, 2025

Welcome to Senter Lite. Your privacy is very important to us. This document explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when using our application.

1. Information We Collect

Senter Lite does not collect or store any personal information from users. The application only requires access to your device's flashlight feature to provide its main function as a flashlight.

2. Required Permissions

To operate the application, we require the following permission:

Camera Access: This permission is necessary to activate and control the flashlight function on your device. We do not use the camera for any purpose other than controlling the flashlight.

3. Use of Information

Since we do not collect personal information, no data is used, shared, or sold to third parties.

4. Security

We are committed to maintaining the security of your device. Senter Lite is designed to function without accessing or storing your personal data.

5. Changes to the Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be communicated through application updates. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.

6. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us via email at support@senterlite.com.
